## 2. Success Metrics (MVP Validation)

### Primary Metrics

* 40â€“50 beta users within 6 weeks
* â‰¥70% weekly Daily Checkâ€‘In completion
* â‰¥60% of users act on at least one proactive nudge per week

### Secondary Indicators

* â‰¥30% reduction in time from insight to action
* Monthly selfâ€‘report of â€œfeeling less overwhelmedâ€
* Weekly reflection completion â‰¥60%

### Kill Metric (Existential Falsifier)

If users report **increased cognitive burden or overwhelm after two weeks**, the MVP is considered failed and must be simplified or halted.

