## 3. Core MVP Features

### Architectural Loop

**Input â†’ Context â†’ Insight â†’ Nudge â†’ Reflection**

All features must reinforce this loop without expanding scope.

---

### Inâ€‘Scope Features

#### Fâ€‘1 Secure Authentication

* Firebase Auth (email/password, optional Google)
* Baseline trust and privacy

#### Fâ€‘2 Structured Daily Checkâ€‘In

* Default: 1 per day
* Userâ€‘modifiable at any time
* AI may *suggest* frequency changes but may not autoâ€‘change

**Fields**:

* Mood (1â€“5)
* Energy (1â€“5)
* Domain ratings (Family, Health, Work, Spiritual: 1â€“3)
* ONE Thing completed (Y/N)
* Optional oneâ€‘sentence reflection (encrypted)

---

#### Fâ€‘3 Contextâ€‘Aware Chat (Aura)

Aura is a **Socratic coaching interface**, not a general chatbot.

**Context Includes**:

* Recent checkâ€‘ins (subject to Context Decay)
* User values and consent flags
* Active Projects (PARA)
* Recent conversation history

**Constraints**:

* Questions before advice
* Frameworkâ€‘grounded (CBT, GTD, 7 Habits)
* No invented data
* Escalation language when distress is detected

---

#### Fâ€‘4 Proactive Nudge Engine

Contextâ€‘triggered prompts designed to reduce avoidance and restore momentum.

**Rules**:

* Max 1 nudge/day, 3/week
* Nudges pause after 3 ignored prompts
* All nudges logged with acknowledgement state

---

#### Fâ€‘5 Weekly Review

Guided 10â€“15 minute reflection:

* Visual summaries (mood/energy)
* Pattern recognition (AIâ€‘assisted)
* Structured questions
* ONE Thing selection

Output saved as timestamped archive entry.

---

#### Fâ€‘6 PARA Dashboard

* Projects: Active / On Hold / Archived
* Areas: Core life domains
* Resources: Notes, insights
* Archives: Completed or dormant material

**Attention Rule**: Only Active Projects are included in AI context or nudging.

