## 8. Risks & Mitigation

* AI overreach â†’ Supervisor veto + constraints
* User overwhelm â†’ Kill metric + nudging limits
* Scope creep â†’ Strict outâ€‘ofâ€‘scope enforcement
* Privacy breach â†’ Encryption + audits

